    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Spirit today is the air that we breathe;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "What thing more important than breathing to do?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For breathing each moment, new life we receive,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And God’s living freshness is constant and new."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For God has been processed, as air now, He’s free;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This life-giving pneuma is all that we need."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s rich and abundant, so plentiful, He,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In spirit to walk is to breathe Him indeed."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "O, say, aren’t you glad that the Spirit’s outpoured"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And God, fully processed, is flowing in us?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So freely we’re breathing this life-giving Lord,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And breathing, receiving His life, glorious!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
